guidance_for_write_dockerfile_agent: The Dockerfile build failed because the GPG key file for the LLVM repository, 'llvm-snapshot.gpg', could not be found at the specified URL (returned a 404 Not Found error). This prevented the repository from being correctly added and subsequent package installations (e.g., clang-11). To fix this, update the GPG key URL in the Dockerfile. Change 'https://apt.llvm.org/llvm-snapshot.gpg' to 'https://apt.llvm.org/llvm-snapshot.gpg.key'. The corrected line should be: `wget -O - https://apt.llvm.org/llvm-snapshot.gpg.key | apt-key add -`.
